{"tid":1512994,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"前線手足寫給前線的話 - 心理戰術","createTime":"2019-08-28T06:33:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T06:58:18.000Z","uid":284583,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cd8b4ad44e793c9ef894c16acda625816737d24b","tid":1512994,"uid":284583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T06:33:14.000Z","msg":"發咁多次夢，成日俾狗追住咬，總有1-2個會跑慢左俾狗追到<br />\n你有冇諗過同狗都可以玩心理戰？成日都會係前面聽到狗狗會細細聲討論，例如<br />\n同事小心，前面好似有人set緊線<br />\n同事小心，遮後面好似有人<br />\n同事小心，前面有人倒野落地<br />\n<br />\n其實狗自身好怕死，所以有時可以做下一啲小動作，令佢地感到衝前的危機會變大，就可以減少佢地9衝咬人的可能啦<br />\n<br />\n無論真set定假set，就在防暴犬出現之時好做了，佢地極可能就在數分鐘內衝前咬人。<br />\n所以 拉魚絲 倒一行水 放多2把遮去遮視線 佢地覺得有伏 就唔太敢跑架啦<br />\n<br />\n狗呢排好喜歡玩圍堵，幾時聚 幾時散 幾時留 幾時跑 手足們要打醒12分精神<br />\n多多留意記者鏡頭方向係邊，就好容易得知邊度有狗(轉角位/隔離街/窄巷)<br />\n<br />\n利申：借朋友ac po"},{"pid":"764347cc6ee187187fb7a2f592c70dfb2407e696","tid":1512994,"uid":284522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T06:33:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/etSapPa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FetSapPa.gif&h=0cba6709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ%2FUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=1f5106ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ%2FUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=76515341\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d